buyerAgent.name: Shelly Salas Your Home Sold Guaranteed

data.description: *Assumable VA Loan @ 5.375%* Welcome to this beautifully maintained home within close proximity to Fort Cavazos and the Killeen-Fort Hood Regional Airport! As you step inside, you are greeted with a beautiful accent wall along a wide hallway which leads into a spacious living room with lots of natural lighting. The entire home has beautiful touches of modern farmhouse elegance with a beautiful accent wall in the living room, trendy light fixtures, and freshly painted white cabinets throughout the home. The master suite features a large room with his and her closets and a large vanity in the master bathroom. The backyard is spacious and includes a covered back patio to enjoy the outdoors in this quiet neighborhood. This home has thoughtful updates you will not want to miss out on! Schedule your showing today!
